|2@{" ", Link CnfNumMeter}  G:240 @{"     # ", Link CnfSliderColor2} |    | |   Vol @{" ", Link CnfMeterType}| @{"   AREXX Macros ...  ",Link CnfAREXXMacros} | @{" Use    ", Link CnfUse} |
